    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个Alice发起群件交易的时序图。核心流程是Alice通过offer-up.contract这个智能合约向Zoe发起交易邀请，涉及KanbanBoard和SprintBacklog两个群件组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "offer-up.contract",
        "Zoe",
        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我打算用三个box来区分角色：aqua色放Alice，darksalmon放Zoe，skyblue放合约。合约激活后向Zoe发邀请，Zoe接受后再返回invitation给合约，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "box aqua",
        "box darksalmon",
        "box skyblue Contract",
        "activate",
        "deactivate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但注意第一步是makeTradeInvitation不是普通invitation，而且Alice发给合约的是异步消息。合约收到后再用makeInvitation转发给Zoe，这时候要带上SprintBacklog。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "makeTradeInvitation",
        "makeInvitation",
        "Groupware_SprintBacklog",
        "async message"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Alice到合约的异步箭头画上，标注makeTradeInvitation(KanbanBoard)。然后合约激活，用虚线箭头异步发给Zoe。Zoe激活后返回invitation，合约再转发Invitation toJoin给Alice。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-)C",
        "C--)Zoe",
        "Zoe--)-C",
        "C--)A",
        "activate C",
        "activate Zoe"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "后半段还有关键步骤：Alice收到邀请后，要向Zoe发起一个offer，这次用的是Groupware_ChatRoom。然后Zoe内部有个escrow Price pmt的处理，最后通过tradeHandler把WikiPage提交回合约。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "offer",
        "Groupware_ChatRoom}",
        "escrow Price pmt",
        "tradeHandler",
        "Groupware_WikiPage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "注意到offer是同步消息，我要用实线加号表示Zoe保持激活。但escrow Price pmt是Zoe自循环，用虚线还是实线？还有tradeHandler之后Zoe要 deactivate 吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-)+Zoe",
        "Zoe--)Zoe",
        "Zoe--)-C",
        "deactivate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "escrow用虚线自循环，tradeHandler之后Zoe确实要关闭。另外合约在第二次激活后也要记得 deactivate，最后只剩合约保持激活状态等待后续处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe--)Zoe",
        "Zoe--)-C",
        "deactivate C",
        "activate C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流程：Alice异步发起交易邀请，合约中转给Zoe，Zoe响应后合约回传邀请，Alice同步提交offer到Zoe，Zoe托管付款后通过tradeHandler把WikiPage交回合约。所有激活和关闭状态都处理好了。",
